     ASSSERTION:Return  all stored progress scores of the student
     ALGORITHM:

     Return progressScores (ArrayList)
     

METHOD: getAverageScore
IMPORT: NONE
EXPORT: averageScore (Double)
ASSERTION: Calculate and return the average score rounded up.

ALGORITHM:

    IF progressScores is empty THEN
        RETURN 0.0
    ENDIF

    SET total = 0

    FOR each score in progressScores DO
        total =total + score
    ENDFOR

    SET average = total / size of progressScores
    SET averageScore = round average up to nearest integer

    RETURN averageScore

    
